{"tid":1636510,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"好似人地勝利咁癡心情長劍咁可以樣樣野都為晒Irene去做，咁樣做對於你來講係侮辱你既智慧係戇居丫嘛","createTime":"2019-10-07T18:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:57:17.000Z","uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"936fbb444adb969be1056c7a18873aa0f6fe7c9b","tid":1636510,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:18:44.000Z","msg":"好似人地勝利咁癡心情長劍咁，<br />\n可以樣樣野都為曬Irene去做，<br />\n咁樣做對於你來講係侮辱你既智慧係戇居丫嘛！<br />\n咁你咪要去抬起其他人囉，<br />\n鍾意去同埋其他女人上床囉！<br />\n<br />\n邊個係我女朋友？我老婆？打工仔來咋！<br />\n<br />\n打工仔？打工仔你使對人咁好個呵？<br />\n<br />\n對邊個好呀而家我呀？<br />\n<br />\n你對邊個好？你對Jennie（金珍妮）唔好咩？<br />\n<br />\n對Jennie仲好！<br />\n<br />\n成街人都睇死你開公司，仲開戲畀佢拍呀！咁多聯絡架？唔洗講野啦我地。<br />\n<br />\n係呀，係以前．．．以前．．．費事嘈呀．．．<br />\n<br />\n我真係恭喜你呀，簽左個娜璉咁蠢西．．．西女人返去！恭喜你快撚Ｄ捧紅佢添呀！<br />\n<br />\n我無諗住要捧佢喎！<br />\n<br />\n你無諗住捧佢簽佢來把撚呀？<br />\n<br />\n咁唔紅果Ｄ．．．咁又簽約．．．"},{"pid":"0820bbb5c774d283097ae05d56aa4e7b7d1df777","tid":1636510,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"又擺我上枱=="},{"pid":"e86b7a2ceb6a83e31809a8b4191ce8694b2000ae","tid":1636510,"uid":165368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168b9e424f8eebe233b0695d629506f06849e526","tid":1636510,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f0545ee1d66bed4d07c1087f0012c6d7a27c7d","tid":1636510,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"召喚李嘉欣同maymay"}]}